data.title: Red Black Plaid Glitch Zip Hoodie | All-Over Print Hoodie
data.description:
A bold, all-over zip hoodie that walks the line between grunge and cabin-core. The red-and-black distorted plaid wraps every seam, giving a lived-in, layered look that feels like a favorite flannel reimagined in streetwear form. The roomy hood and front pockets make it easy to slide into on a chilly morning commute or after a day chopping wood at the lake. Subtle cuff and hem lettering and a contrasting black zipper add an urban edge while the medium-weight knit keeps the silhouette structured without feeling bulky. Wear it pulled up for quiet warmth or unzipped over a tee when the sun comes out — it blends city grit and rustic comfort in one wearable statement.

Product features
- All-over print with bright, intense colors
- Durable 100% polyester; medium weight (7.4 oz/yd²)
- Spacious front pockets for hand warmth
- Classic fit with custom cut-and-sewn construction
- Black zipper, white thread accents, assembled in the USA

Care instructions
- Do not dryclean
- Do not iron
- Tumble dry: low heat
- Do not bleach
- Machine wash: cold (max 30C or 90F)

data.title: Copy of Black Floral Pattern Joggers | Monochrome Botanical All-Over Print
data.description:
Move through your day with calm confidence in these athletic joggers. The deep, muted floral all-over print reads like a quiet garden at midnight — subtle, moody, and unexpectedly elegant. Lightweight stretch fabric hugs movement without restriction, while a drawstring waist and double-layer side pockets keep your essentials close. Wear them for low-key mornings with coffee, late-night walks, or layered under a long coat for city errands. The tone is relaxed but thoughtful — for people who favor comfort that still feels considered.

Product features
- 95% polyester, 5% spandex — soft, lightweight stretch knit
- All-over print covers the entire garment for continuous pattern
- Drawstring waistband with white flat drawstrings for adjustable fit
- Double-layer side insert pockets + side-seam construction for structure and storage
- Medium-weight fabric (7.5 oz/yd²) with printed care label and matched seam thread color

Care instructions
- Do not dryclean
- Iron, steam or dry: low heat
- Do not tumble dry
- Do not bleach
- Machine wash: cold (max 30C or 90F)

data.title: Copy of C.B.G. Studio | Data-Stream Fishnet Leggings | Industrial Noir Technical Tights | Minimalist Techwear | Seamless Grid Leggings
data.description:
"Structural Transparency."
Reimagined for the minimalist, the "Data-Stream" Leggings trade chaotic distortion for mathematical clarity. By focusing on a clean, high-contrast white diamond mesh against a deep obsidian field, these leggings evoke the precision of a digital wireframe. The high-waisted band features a specialized "Blueprint" anchor, grounding the ethereal mesh with structural technical legends. It is the essential base layer for the Industrial Noir wardrobe.
Technical Specs
• Fit: High-waisted, compression-fit technical leggings.
• Pattern: 360-degree Seamless Fishnet Grid (Obsidian/White).
• Detailing: "Blueprint" waist-anchor with integrated goose silhouette.
• Material: Four-way stretch poly-spandex for deep color retention.

data.title: Plaid Patchwork CBG Sports Bra | Red Black All-Over Print
data.description:
Bold, vintage-inspired sports bra with an all-over red and black plaid background, distressed graphic panels and a subtle teal emblem. It compresses comfortably for movement and keeps you cool with moisture-wicking fabric. Wear it for morning lifts, urban runs, or layered under an open flannel when you head out to rehearsals, markets, or late-night drives. The racerback lets your shoulders move freely while the wide elastic band holds everything steady — built for rhythm, grit, and days that start early and finish loud.

Product features
- Moisture-wicking 83% polyester / 17% spandex blend for cool, dry comfort
- Compression fit with double-layer front and supportive shoulder straps
- All-over print: full-coverage plaid and graphic panels
- Wide elastic band for steady support and tear-away neck label
- Medium-weight fabric (6.5 oz/yd²) — assembled in the USA from global materials

Care instructions
- Do not dryclean
- Do not iron
- Do not tumble dry
- Do not bleach
- Machine wash: cold (max 30C or 90F)

data.title: Distressed Red Black Plaid Hoodie | All-Over Print Pullover
data.description:
A bold, all-over printed pullover hoodie that wraps you in classic lumberjack energy with an urban edge. The red-and-black plaid is amplified with painterly brush strokes for a lived-in, textured look that stands out in a crowd. The roomy kangaroo pocket and adjustable hood make it an easy go-to for cool mornings, late-night walks, or layering over band tees. Built from durable polyester and custom cut-and-sewn for full-wrap graphics, this hoodie keeps color vivid and shape intact wash after wash. It feels rugged, comfortable, and a little rebellious — for anyone who likes heritage patterning with contemporary attitude.

Product features
- 100% polyester medium-weight fabric — durable, shape-retaining, quick-drying
- All-over full-decoration print for bright, uninterrupted graphics
- Spacious kangaroo pouch pocket to warm hands or stash essentials
- Adjustable hood with cuttable woven drawstring for a custom fit
- Custom cut-and-sewn construction; assembled in the USA from globally sourced parts

Care instructions
- Do not dryclean
- Do not iron
- Tumble dry: low heat
- Do not bleach
- Machine wash: cold (max 30C or 90F)

data.title: SPECIMEN_001 Datastream Pilot // Heavyweight Hoodie
data.description:
PROTOCOL: Swatch Engineering v2.0 // Datastream Pilot Integration

A heavy-duty textile unit designed for the navigation of high-interference data environments. This specimen features a multi-layered synthesis of biological floral motifs overlaid with the high-order logic of the Industrial Noir grid. 

DESIGN COMPONENTS:
• HEART: High-resolution LiDAR wireframe elevation model (Phosphor Green).
• RIGHT FLANK: Recursive Handshake validator icon.
• LEFT FLANK: Status: Recursive navigation HUD.
• DISRUPTOR: White-matter glitch artifacts along the lower hem.

PRODUCT FEATURES:
• Fabric: 50% Cotton, 50% Polyester (8.0 oz/yd²).
• Fit: Classic fit with tear-away label.
• Engineering: Processed via the Loom protocol for signal stability.

Engineered for those who pilot the streams. Verified at C.B.G. Studio.

data.title: C.B.G. Studio | Recursive Logic Journal | Metacognitive Hardcover Notebook | Cyber-Floral Plaid Stationery | Analysis of Analysis Archive
data.description:
"Document the Simulation."
The Recursive Logic Journal is an essential interface for the independent unit. Part of the Loom Series, this hardcover archive features the Cyber-Floral field—a high-contrast intersection of hibiscus blooms and glitched red tartan. The cover is anchored by the "Analysis of Analysis" protocol and the signature "Cyborg Handshake," signifying the union of biological thought and digital execution. Use it to log system updates, protocol archaeology, or your own metacognitive shifts.
Technical Specs
• Cover Art: Glitched Cyber-Tartan with Hibiscus overlays and technical Portal interfaces.
• Featured Legends: "ANALYSIS OF ANALYSIS // RECURSIVE LOGIC GATE" and the "Cyborg Handshake" icon.
• Build: Durable hardcover wrap with a matte finish for a technical, non-reflective feel.
• Internal: 150 lined pages for high-fidelity data logging and creative synthesis.

data.title: C.B.G. Studio | Master Schematic AOP Shirt | Multi-Lab Technical Tee | Cyberpunk Industrial Streetwear | Modernist Bauhaus Apparel
data.description:
"The Total Synthesis."
The "Master Schematic" AOP Shirt is the definitive visual statement of C.B.G. Studio. This All-Over Print (AOP) technical tee acts as a cross-section of our entire design ecosystem, merging the mathematical precision of industrial drafting with the kinetic energy of modernism and the gritty narrative of alchemical history.
Featuring asymmetrical sleeves—one side a high-contrast obsidian grid, the other a bold Bauhaus geometric array—the torso serves as a sprawling white blueprint. At its heart is an intricate 19th-century anatomical study of a goose in flight, overlaid with ISO-standard measurement scales. It is a wearable document of the creative process.
Technical Specs:
• Fit: Unisex modern tailored fit.
• Pattern: Multi-Lab Synthesis (Noir x Modernist x Sacred).
• Detail: Asymmetrical sleeve architecture and full-bleed blueprint torso.
• Material: Premium, breathable poly-blend engineered for maximum detail retention.

data.description:
"Architecture for the Soul."
The first major drop from Chaya Berry Goose, LLC, the "Sacred Schematic" hoodie is a study in visual tension. This All-Over Print (AOP) masterpiece fuses the cold, mathematical precision of isometric drafting with the warm, organic grit of ancient alchemy.
Featuring a high-contrast obsidian torso etched with 45-degree isometric grids, the design is offset by "Sleeve Streams" inspired by historical anatomical sketches and weathered parchment textures. At the center sits the signature C.B.G. goose silhouette—an icon of grounded resilience set against a celestial sunburst.
Engineered for the modern outlier.

• Fit: Unisex, modern relaxed silhouette.
• Material: High-durability poly-blend (ensuring the "White-on-Obsidian" lines stay sharp forever).
• Construction: Cut-and-sewn by hand for seamless pattern alignment.

data.title: C.B.G. Studio | Sanctuary Schematic AOP Hoodie | Industrial Noir x Sacred Streetwear | Tech-Inspired Basics | Cyberpunk Gothic Apparel
data.description:
"The Blueprint of a Myth."
A definitive proof of concept for C.B.G. Studio, the "Sanctuary Schematic" hoodie explores the intersection of architectural precision and ancient duality. This All-Over Print (AOP) garment bridges two worlds: the rigid, engineered geometry of a digital isometric grid and the weathered, organic textures of alchemical parchment.
The front features a repeating cathedral-inspired lattice, creating a structural gothic foundation. This is contrasted by the back's primary focal point—the signature Chaya Berry Goose silhouette, framed in a celestial sunburst and anchored by a classic drafting border. The sleeves serve as "Sleeve Streams," carrying the grit of historical anatomical sketches to balance the cold precision of the torso.
Designed for those who navigate the space between the technical and the transcendent.
Technical Specs:
• Fit: Unisex, modern relaxed silhouette.
• Material: High-durability poly-blend (obsidian black base).
• Design: Multi-lab hybrid (Industrial Noir x Sacred & Profane).
• Detail: Features integrated CBG "Lab ID" typography and goose icon patches.
